    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at 3rd level, you have gained access to a special quiver that your family has made for generations. Using fuinjutsu, your quiver can hold an almost infinite amount of ammo. Your ammunition die starts at a d12 and any time a feature or jutsu would require you to use all of your ammunition you instead reduce your ammunition die step by 1.</p>",
